<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">    &quot;type&quot;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">: </span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;string (可选，默认 auto，常见值 feat/fix/refactor/docs/chore)&quot;</span></span>
